<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTPA1">
<l>pallāṇṭu pāllāṇṭu pallā yirattāṇṭu</l>
<l rend="indent">palkōṭi nūṟā yiram</l>
<l>mallāṇṭa tiṇṭōḷ maṇivaṇ ṇāvuṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">cevvaṭi cevvitiruk kāppu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Many years, many years, many thousands of years,</l>
<l rend="indent">many millions of hundreds of thousands</l>
<l>Sapphire hued Lord with strong shoulders that dominate [in] wrestling</l>
<l rend="indent">the beauty of your red feet is [our] divine protection.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
